code: @Override public void process(Exchange exchange) throws Exception {     Object body = exchange.getIn().getBody().     if (body instanceof Object[]) {         Object[] args = (Object[]) body.         if (args.length == 2 && args[0] instanceof Key && args[1] instanceof Value) {             keyValue.put((Key) args[0], (Value) args[1]).         }     } }
public void setKeyValue(KeyValueProtocol keyValue) {     this.keyValue = keyValue. }
